document.discussion_title: Lovely Photos From Omotola's Son's 18th Birthday Party - OliviasGist
document.topic_text:
Lovely Photos From Omotola’s Son’s 18th Birthday Party August 22, 2016 20 Omotola’s first daughter Princess, and media personality Denrele were pictured on her brother’s 18th birthday goofing around.
They look adorable. See more photos from Omotola’s son birthday party after the cut. Mike Ezuruonye, Sound Sultan, Patoranking, Swanky Jerry, Rukky Sanda and others were in attendance.
